一次驗眼時唔知原來隻左眼咁差 一遮住右眼驗時 嘩咗一聲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c9146068bf352de4b2c9776f7168cf16c45b0a","tid":2275552,"uid":207254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"我左右眼差幾百度<br />\n嚴重嗰隻近視 另一隻散光<br />\n初初帶眼鏡半個鐘就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a367243267be5b08951c8a88972611689f7b38","tid":2275552,"uid":21836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c9146068bf352de4b2c9776f7168cf16c45b0a","tid":2275552,"uid":207254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"我左右眼差幾百度<br />\n嚴重嗰隻近視 另一隻散光<br />\n初初帶眼鏡半個鐘就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"我都係，嚴重左眼遠視加散光<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6188c177e5533c7c51965985cd507666926cd40c","tid":2275552,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"block咗幾位懶幽默嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都有樓主個情況 但想知照鏡會唔會睇得出 (e.g. 大細眼？）<br />\n前排有人講激光矯視弊端 勁多人覆 所以冇諗過要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91af2c753513c00ec60bd88040e3045242f307fd","tid":2275552,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"右眼有嚴重眼疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392032b8c15c86d2641af6536bd332cbc798ae26","tid":2275552,"uid":271334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"懶惰眼<br />\n<br />\n細個睇視科 有叫我阻住隻眼一段時間<br />\n但幼稚園貪靚 無跟住咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加習慣睇野用開其中一隻眼<br />\n另一隻眼視力差好多<br />\n<br />\n利申 做過smile  問過醫生<br />\n懶惰眼要7歲前處理好"},{"pid":"4b9b321c18a5c84de6faa5c6b46b5a